### Sequencing

1. Tighten manifest schemas (Step 1) — this is a breaking schema change; do it first so all downstream code sees the right types.
2. Extend `AgentConfig` and `AgentProvenance` in `types.ts` (Step 2) — types drive everything else.
3. Populate agents registry (Step 3) — depends on Step 2.
